Hello Kristinn, thanks for the feedback!

The cxml that you found is the default starting config for new jobs 
created via the web interface. (The easiest way to get at it is to 
create a new job.) The other one that used to be in there was merely a 
redundant copy. See https://webarchive.jira.com/browse/HER-1856

Thanks for reporting that obsolete setting commented out in the default 
config. It&#39;s gone now - 
https://webarchive.jira.com/source/changelog/HER/?cs=7233

Normally we update the default cxml whenever we make settings changes in 
the code. This one was an oversight.

Noah

